`https://aliasanvil.com/v2buofj3GtkNgN5i_HpKdhXQcR0H-0FUXZz8Ve2S2SeH7GuEEL3YrWAc` from https://github.com/uBlockOrigin/uAssets/issues/16731 - not caught
